# Cookie Policy for Afterparty Bots
Last Updated: January 20, 2026

At **Afterparty Bots** (“we,” “our,” “us”), we value your privacy and are committed to being transparent about how we use cookies and similar technologies to collect information when you interact with our Bots (VERSA, Afterparty Groovy Music, Lofi Vibes, VoiceMaestro, VerifyBot, KitsuBot, The Guardian Link).

This Cookie Policy explains what cookies are, how we use them, and the choices you have regarding their use.

## 1. What Are Cookies?
Cookies are small text files placed on your device when you visit a website or use an online service. These files help the service recognize your device and improve your experience by remembering preferences, login details, and other settings.

## 2. Types of Cookies We Use
- **Essential Cookies:** Required for our bots to function (e.g., moderation features, role management, playback).
- **Analytics Cookies:** May be set by third parties (e.g., Discord analytics, bot management tools) to understand usage and improve performance.
- **Performance Cookies:** Help us monitor uptime, diagnose issues, and optimize performance.

## 3. How We Use Cookies
- **Improve Functionality:** Remember preferences and settings.
- **Monitor Performance:** Understand interactions to improve experience.
- **Analyze Usage:** Track aggregate trends to guide future updates.

## 4. Your Cookie Choices
You can control cookies via your browser’s privacy settings. Disabling cookies may affect certain features. For Discord-based interactions, cookie and privacy preferences can also be managed in Discord’s own settings.

## 5. Third-Party Cookies
Our bots may interact with third-party services (e.g., Discord, analytics providers) who may set their own cookies under their privacy policies. We don’t control third-party cookies.

## 6. Changes to this Cookie Policy
We may update this policy to reflect changes in technology, legal requirements, or our services. Significant changes will be announced on our website or Discord server.

## 7. Contact Us
Questions? Email us at [support@afterpartylabs.xyz](mailto:support@afterpartylabs.xyz).
